response.homeDescription: Beautiful Custom Home located in Central Community. This like-new 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath home with split floor plan features stained concrete floors and granite countertops throughout, a gorgeous exposed brick gas fireplace, open concept living areas, a formal dining room and an eat-in kitchen, plus a huge bonus room. Kitchen features all stainless steel appliances, spacious corner pantry, and a center island with additional storage, butcher block bar top, and seating for 3. The Master Bedroom has an en suite bath with a custom tile shower, soaker tub, water closet, double vanities, and a wrap-around walk-in closet. First floor also has laundry room, two additional bedrooms with walk-in closets and a full bath with double vanities and linen closet. Second floor features fourth bedroom and a spacious bonus room which would be perfect for a playroom, media room, hobby room, office, or an additional family space. Home is also equipped with a security system and surround sound. Schedule a showing today, this is truly a MUST SEE!
